un shabes ze'mir aroysgegangen oyf der gas,

00:18:16.127 --> 00:18:26.283
tsu eynem, tsum tsveytn, zikh nokh trefn, ikh hob getrofn di mume, ikh hob getrofn. dort iz gevezn a gantse KIBUTZ bay mayn mume, ver s'iz gekumen, a yeder ot dort, zey zenen arayn in zeyer shtub,

00:18:26.283 --> 00:18:31.208
zey hobn, me hot gekokht, me hot ge- me hot me hot a yedn gevart un

