un azoy vi ikh bin aroys oyf der gas, hob ikh bakumen a shreklekhn

00:18:36.462 --> 00:18:39.470
atak, a kremf fun fus,

00:18:39.470 --> 00:18:41.754
ober ikh hob mikh mer nisht gekont rirn.

00:18:42.874 --> 00:18:46.007
un demolts hot mikh mayn tate avekgefirt tsun zeyer a

00:18:46.519 --> 00:18:48.144
gevislekhn

00:18:48.144 --> 00:18:51.221
profesor, er hot geheysn profesor Liner,

00:18:51.582 --> 00:18:53.061
a ortoped.

