dos iz geven a shtot

00:18:56.222 --> 00:18:58.578
Berehove, Bereksaz.

00:18:58.652 --> 00:19:00.907
un er hot mikh tsun im avekgefirt,

00:19:01.251 --> 00:19:04.485
un er hot mikh zofort arayngeleygt in gips arayn,

00:19:05.605 --> 00:19:08.436
vos er hot mikh gehaltn zeks khadoshim.

00:19:08.436 --> 00:19:11.842
vayl er hot mikh gevolt operirn demolts,

00:19:12.625 --> 00:19:16.787
un nor s'iz nisht gegan der operatsye, ober mir ho'mir farpast

00:19:17.620 --> 00:19:21.548
dos aroysgeyn fun Rusland. vi lang ikh bin gelegn dort

00:19:21.548 --> 00:19:24.195
hot men farshpart ale grenetsn.

00:19:26.023 --> 00:19:29.291
un keyn feygl hot mer nisht gekont aroysflien fun

00:19:29.955 --> 00:19:35.467
fun Rusl- vayl dos iz demolts geven, undz ze'mir aheymgekumen funem lager ho'mir undz getrofn dortn rusn

00:19:36.942 --> 00:19:40.311
bazetst, in finef un fertsiker yor hobn zey bazetst dort.

00:19:41.245 --> 00:19:45.424
un zey hobn farmakht di grenetsn. mayne khavertes

00:19:45.835 --> 00:19:49.626
zenen gekumen fun, mikh bazukhn in shpitol,

00:19:49.918 --> 00:19:53.169
un zey hobn gebetn, "blayb nisht Rokhele do a ton!"

00:19:53.344 --> 00:19:58.586
ober ikh bin gevezn opgebundn, ikh hob nisht gekont mikh rirn, ikh hob ge- ikh bin geven in shpitol.

00:19:59.487 --> 00:20:03.238
un azoy ze'mir undz farblibn dort,

00:20:03.238 --> 00:20:05.404
zibn un tsvontsik yor.

00:20:06.777 --> 00:20:12.070
