00:20:12.312 --> 00:20:15.017
ikh hob nisht gekont oyshaltn keyn operatsye.

00:20:15.017 --> 00:20:17.115
er hot mikh afile shoyn farshleft,

00:20:17.205 --> 00:20:20.053
ober er hot gezen az dos harts vet es mir nisht oyshaltn,

00:20:20.053 --> 00:20:22.683
hot er zikh opgelozt fun der operatsye,

00:20:23.533 --> 00:20:26.615
un ven ikh bin aheymgekumen

00:20:27.077 --> 00:20:32.960
fun der shpitol, hot mayn tate, iz er shoyn gevezn vos m'hot ongerufn in Rusland,

00:20:33.253 --> 00:20:39.559
khulak, dos heyst a raykher. an oysher.

00:20:41.590 --> 00:20:45.111
er hot nisht gevust az er hot fir mit di rusn,

00:20:46.045 --> 00:20:48.317
s'mit di rusn kon men zikh nisht shpiln.

00:20:49.656 --> 00:20:52.614
ven undz ze'mir aheymgekumen, hot men undzere shtub,

00:20:52.614 --> 00:20:54.138
iz arayngefaln,

00:20:54.280 --> 00:20:56.383
dos iz geven bay der grenets.

00:20:56.997 --> 00:20:59.353
un s'arayngefaln far di

00:21:00.051 --> 00:21:05.377
rusishe soldatn hobn dos tsugenumen undzere shtiber bay di grenets, un zey hobn dos bazetst.

00:21:05.772 --> 00:21:09.124
un zey hobn gezogt, se geven tsebrokhene shtiber in shtot,

00:21:09.501 --> 00:21:12.296
nemts aykh velkhe shtiber ets vilt,

00:21:12.505 --> 00:21:13.832
a yidishe,

00:21:13.973 --> 00:21:16.312
un bazetst aykh dort voynen.

00:21:17.078 --> 00:21:23.957
mayn hot zeyer a groyser BUSINESS mentsh gevezn demolts, er hot opgekoyft ales fun di rusishe soldatn

00:21:24.098 --> 00:21:26.117
far fleshlekh bronfn.

00:21:26.697 --> 00:21:28.766
vayl zey hobn zeyer getrunken

00:21:28.857 --> 00:21:34.504
un se gevezn der poyern hobn gekokht di bronfns fun epl un fun floymen,

00:21:34.527 --> 00:21:41.541
er hot dos bay zey opgekoyft, er hot gegebn far zey, er hot opgevart di groyse vagonen vos zey hobn gefirt, ongepakte,

00:21:41.817 --> 00:21:45.540
mit gold un mit alemen vos zey hobn aroysgefirt fun di,

00:21:46.339 --> 00:21:51.058
fun Tshekhay, fun fun ale zaytn, fun Daytshland, fun fun ale zaytn.

