00:22:05.408 --> 00:22:10.346
in shtot, eyn eyntsiks, vos keyner hot dos nisht oyfgemakht bay di shlakht.

00:22:10.808 --> 00:22:14.379
un dos iz geven a gesheft fun gesh- -shirn,

00:22:14.503 --> 00:22:16.252
fun geshir vos me kokht,

00:22:16.360 --> 00:22:19.408
mit glozene zakhn, mit azolkhe zakhn.

00:22:20.157 --> 00:22:25.939
