ikh bin geshtanen, undzer shtub iz gevezn in mitn der shtot.

00:27:14.723 --> 00:27:17.994
ikh hob gezen vi azoy m'breng tsu fri mentshn vos me hot gekhapt

00:27:18.051 --> 00:27:19.583
un me firt zey arayn.

00:27:19.583 --> 00:27:22.247
un ikh bin geshtanen un ikh hob gevart.

00:27:22.877 --> 00:27:27.090
ven er iz avekgeganen iz gevezn bayn undz dershmuest,

00:27:27.957 --> 00:27:35.140
ikh hob gegebn a signal, mayn signal hot nisht gevust, mayn tate's signal hot nisht gevust keyner, nor ikh un der tate.

00:27:35.753 --> 00:27:38.121
un ven i- me hot ge- ven.

00:27:38.121 --> 00:27:40.488
un der vos er hot,

00:27:41.338 --> 00:27:47.424
ven der, ven a mentsh iz gekumen mitn tate's signal az me hot im durkhgefirt mit dem nomen,

00:27:47.582 --> 00:27:49.365
ikh hob poshet gezogt

00:27:49.624 --> 00:27:53.854
a shpor, dos heyst hot geheysn, haynt heyst es a gaz. shpor.

00:27:54.096 --> 00:27:56.705
un ven ikh hob bakumen dos tsetele shpor,

00:27:57.522 --> 00:28:02.724
demolts hot der mentsh vu dos gelt iz geven aropgeleygt hot men batsolt far deye mentshn

00:28:02.724 --> 00:28:06.442
dos gelt, az mayn tate iz aribergegangen dos grenetsn.

00:28:06.972 --> 00:28:09.176
mayn tate iz shoyn nisht geven in Rusland.

00:28:12.017 --> 00:28:14.638
mayn tate hot men gekhapt oyf a por pletser,

00:28:14.638 --> 00:28:17.225
ober er hot zikh oysgekoyft, er hot gehat,

00:28:17.839 --> 00:28:23.385
vayl deye nakht, befor er iz geforn, hot men a gantse nakht geneyt dos gold arayn in di,

00:28:23.813 --> 00:28:28.763
un mit dem hot er zikh oysgekoyft, vayl er iz nisht avek nor mit a kleyne tashke

00:28:28.763 --> 00:28:31.243
vos er hot zikh getrogn a tseyn bershtl mit

00:28:31.243 --> 00:28:33.307
ibertsutun tsvey mol zakhn.

00:28:33.938 --> 00:28:36.863
azoy vi er zol aroysgeyn fun der shtub, vayl er hot gezogt

00:28:36.863 --> 00:28:39.495
az er geyt makhn keyn Kiev

00:28:39.495 --> 00:28:42.386
an APPELATION oyfn COURT,

00:28:42.595 --> 00:28:44.496
az er fort avek azoy.

00:28:44.535 --> 00:28:47.836
bayn undz in tsveytn tog hot men shoyn ibergekert der gantse shtub,

00:28:48.889 --> 00:28:50.587
di rusishe ofitsirn,

00:28:51.302 --> 00:28:58.063
m'hot undz shoyn geshtelt antkegn biksn. ikh vel nisht konen dos dertseyln vos zey hobn mit undz getun ale yorn.

00:28:58.137 --> 00:29:01.323
zey hobn undz nisht gegebn keyn arbet, zey hobn undz aroysgevorfn fun di sh-

00:29:01.323 --> 00:29:05.285
undz ze'mir durkhgegangen dem tsveytn lager in Rusland,

00:29:05.663 --> 00:29:10.613
mit tsvey kinder, shver, shver.

00:29:10.613 --> 00:29:12.764
ikh bin aroyfgegan nisht eyn mol

00:29:12.764 --> 00:29:16.777
oyvn oyf di partey vu me hot zikh, vu ikh hob mikh arayngerisn mit di kinder,

00:29:16.817 --> 00:29:19.142
un ikh hob gezogt, ikh sam op di kinder,

00:29:19.142 --> 00:29:24.610
ikh sam op mikh. der tate hot gelebt zayn lebn, ikh leb mayn lebn,

00:29:24.610 --> 00:29:26.464
un ets hot nisht keyn rekht

00:29:26.487 --> 00:29:30.767
mikh tsu shteln antkegn pistolet un mikh tsu shte- un mayn man tsu shteln.

00:29:30.975 --> 00:29:37.587
un az mikh hot nisht geharget Mengele, ikh vel mikh fun aykh nisht lozn hargenen, ober ikh vel mikh hargenen aleyn un mayne kinder oykhet.

00:29:38.468 --> 00:29:41.232
me vel oyfhern yetst un makhn nokh oystoysh.
